title: Bhama Rukmani
subTitle: While Bhama loves Nandagopal and wishes to marry him, his heart belongs to Rukmani. Complications arise when he ends up marrying both women.

title: Maya Bazaar

title: Thotta Chinungi
subTitle: Gopal does not like that his wife, Bhuvana, is friends with Mano and gets suspicious about her. However, he realizes his mistake and makes amends.

title: Sivakaasi

title: Chinna Kannamma

title: Mundravathu Kann
subTitle: A young woman trapped in her home accidentally records a horrific crime next door, triggering a dangerous game of cat and mouse as the killer tries to silence her.
